<br>
His "blips" as you call them have the potential to make people very physically ill. &nbsp;The loss of human life and the amount of hatred being thrown around here aren't things to play around with. &nbsp;His comments aren't the typical "rouse the crowd" comments that people throw around just to start flamewars. &nbsp;People are dead. &nbsp;Many are fearing nuclear consequences. &nbsp;Joking about how this is a good thing due to "population control" or "more available jobs" is in such bad taste that I'd rather see Jevert and Inviticus running around blabbing. &nbsp;This situation doesn't just affect people in New York City; Washington, D.C.; or the other sites of crashes. &nbsp;This is nationwide, and this is worldwide. &nbsp;My friends and family in different countries are both in mourning over people they know and also anxious about what's to come. &nbsp;Multiple countries have closed down air travel and are checking their own defense statuses. &nbsp;That is how serious it is.<br>
<br>
